Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,DECISION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,DEATH NOTE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby relinquish ownership\Nof this Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers quietly]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[moans]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Mr. Stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do-- do you think we could stop this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] Huh?\N-[Aizawa] "Stalker?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the new attitude\Nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I still have Ryuk's notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I gave up Rem's,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all awareness I have of Rem still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I have to go through\Nall this trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is because you brought another Death Note\Nto the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really what you want, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I never thought\Nthe Death Note I gave you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,would end up buried and abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Ryuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for the time being\NI'm just hiding it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it stays mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the next time\Nyou hear me say the following words:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,regardless of the context,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,assume that I want to relinquish\Nownership of this Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Stalker, this is illegal.\NYou have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been acting like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since she regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she think she can get out of this\Njust by playing dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Okay. How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least take off my blindfold,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice to see\Nwhat you look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, call Mogi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone keys beep]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mogi, when you apprehended Misa Amane,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you made it clear\Nthat she was a suspect. Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Like you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I blindfolded her\Nand covered her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I... told her we knew\Nshe was the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure that she heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't struggle when I\Nput the blindfold and handcuffs on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like... she accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I give you an autograph\Nor shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I can give you\Na kiss on the cheek if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. I won't run away. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already made\Nso much progress with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually thought she'd crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she suddenly talking\Nabout a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] [modified voice] Misa Amane.\N-[Misa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Mr. Stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to release me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] [modified voice] Before you\Npassed out, you barely spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you even asked me to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're claiming ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're the one who knocked me out\Nand brought me here, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. This is some kind of Misa Amane\Ninterrogation fantasy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I'm detaining you here?\NYou must have some idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] What do you mean?\NBecause I'm a celebrity, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you’re definitely the first stalker\Nwho's ever gone this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're starting to scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Amane, no one is buying this!\NSo, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. This is scary. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it anymore!\NPlease, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to the bathroom again! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] [modified voice]\NIt's only been four minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,since you last went to the bathroom.\NI'm afraid, you'll have to hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only time you'll untie me\Nand let me move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, you'll be able to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you want, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a... pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane, let's get back to the conversation\Nwe were having
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,before you lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all,\Ndo you know who Light Yagami is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, why did you approach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NHow can I not know my own boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] She was so tight-lipped\Nabout it earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but now she's openly admitting\Nhe's her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-[L] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing. It's Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, turn the video and audio off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Yagami] Yes.\N-[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes. Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be expecting you in room K2801.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying my son's coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, like I said over the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you even say\Nsomething like that? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] There's no real proof\Nthat Light Yagami is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why come here to announce\Nthat you could be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "could be" about it.\NYou are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you hope\Nto accomplish by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Dad, if Ryuzaki is L,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's safe to say\Nthat he is the world's best detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, he seems pretty sure\Nthat I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We know L's never been wrong before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-- What are you saying, Light?\NStop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What about that FBI agent,\NRaye Penber?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me he was investigating\Nimmediately before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was in Aoyama on May 22nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'm the first person\Nin the Kanto region
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that Misa, the alleged\NSecond Kira, approached.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all been me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in L's place, even I\Nwould have come to the same conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, subconsciously I might be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were the case,\NI could be him and not even know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're not conscious of it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm not sure of anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never kill someone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,unconsciously, who knows\Nwhat I'm capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Another me could be killing people\Nas I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Not possible? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I never mentioned this to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but at one point I had hidden\Nsurveillance cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,installed in your room for five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single night you slept normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminals, whose names were broadcast,\Nwere still dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you would have had no way\Nof knowing about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But this didn't prove your innocence\Nto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All it proved was\Nthat if you were Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,no amount of camera surveillance\Nwould reveal that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't reveal that fact, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't know. It could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found myself thinking that…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,some criminals deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can think like Kira,\Nthan how can I be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm not actually him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel exactly the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found myself thinking before\Nthat some people would be better off dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, that doesn't mean\Nwe're gonna go out and kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, criminals were still being killed\Neven while you had no knowledge of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the surveillance cameras\Nproved it, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we were\Nshort of investigators then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we only watched him while he was at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is, we weren't able to watch him\Nevery hour of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible he could've found some way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill those criminals\Nwhile he wasn't at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] This was premeditated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no accident you chose to do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what if we incarcerate\Nyou for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Imprison you, like we did Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If criminals whose names were made public,\Nkeep dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then it would lead us to think\Nthat you're innocent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you imagined it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Honestly, I don't like the way\Nthat this is going at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But what choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to fully restrain Light Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and place him in solitary confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to confine him? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If we're gonna do this,\Nit has to happen immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point on you can't be allowed\Nto go anywhere where I can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way my son could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My son is not capable of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's okay, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Something has to be done about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm having these doubts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't work with you to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,promise me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you can say\Nwith absolute certainty that I'm not Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot set me free,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what I might say,\Nor what condition I might be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami, can you come up with some\Nsort of excuse for Light’s absence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,something to tell your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And... please, do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But... this is all so sudden.\NWhat should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I see no reason\Nwhy he should be in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let it go, Dad.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do this,\NI won't be able to live with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But son, do you really... mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that by giving up\Nmy very freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat this fear\Nthat Kira lurks within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Aizawa, please, take him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[prison gates slam]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,FIRST DAY IN PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I just have to\Nget rid of the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess apples\Nare out of the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to request that you take me\Noff this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief!\N-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought about this and the fact is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're holding my son, Light,\Nas a prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that, it's not appropriate for me\Nto be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When we spoke earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,my feelings got in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for me to be objective\Nin this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let personal feelings\Nget in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And in truth... if...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,if the task force concludes\Nthat my son is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'd be capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes, I'll agree with you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI wondered what you might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you'd kill your son\Nand then yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd also agree that it's best
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that we don't have you\Nworking here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask that you confine me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, I'm calm,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but to be honest, I'm not sure\Nhow much more of this I can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might say that,\Nso I spoke with Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's made arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda and Aizawa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm. But your confinement\Nwill be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You will keep your cell phone turned on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and maintain regular contact\Nwith family and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't tell Light about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does call you at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,he must be made to believe\Nthat you're still at headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,While you are in confinement,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be giving you\Ncontinuous updates on the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'll know what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how does that sound to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,THIRD DAY IN PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Hey, Mister,\NI really wanna take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure you already know\Nwhere I live, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you bring me some clean clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this could get\Nany more bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for the Chief right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any new criminals been identified?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone that Kira would be\Nlikely to target?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, has he killed any of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, quite a few criminals' names\Nhave been broadcast recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you've been detained
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't had one report\Nof a criminal being killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no one's been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's only a matter of time\Nbefore I'm convicted as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wouldn't give for an apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the murders would continue\Neven after Light was confined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,they've stopped completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Light asked to be confined\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it will only strengthen\Nthe argument that he is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only question left
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,will be whether or not\Nhe was conscious of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he really think that's gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That he will be let off the hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if he can just prove\Nhe wasn't conscious of being Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,FIFTH DAY IN PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get an apple soon,\NI don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I just have\Nto get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Mr. Stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,your video won't sell if it's just me\Nsitting here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Mr. Yagami looks pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's taking this harder\Nthan Light or Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five days\Nsince Light was put in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And look, not a single criminal\Nwhose name has been broadcast was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In these situations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the parents must suffer\Na lot more than the accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially now that we're seeing proof\Nthat Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Is it good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda and Aizawa groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I wanted to tell you\Nnot to worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how much time\Nyou devote to worrying about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The outcome will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This could go on for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should rest\Nin a more comfortable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!\NWhat makes you think I care where I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With the state I'm in now,\Nthis is the best place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And no matter what the results,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when I leave here\Nit's going to be with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,SEVENTH DAY IN PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, you've only been here\Nfor one week,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure it can't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Now, that I've come this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know I must look\Npretty bad in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but this useless pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-[grunts]\N-[chains jangling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that I was the one\Npushing for confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I asked you to put me in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just realized something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing is completely pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[Light] Because I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised you that no matter\Nwhat you said, I wouldn't let you out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,until I was convinced\Nthat you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, L. I wasn’t thinking clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think\Nthat a serial killer like Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,could commit those crimes\Nwithout being aware of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have no memory of his crimes,\NI'm not him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never been able\Nto accept this idea
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kira has been acting\Nwithout self-awareness all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't change that fact
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that all the evidence\Npoints to you being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we imprisoned you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira hasn't committed a single murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, just hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to you, I am not lying.\NYou have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have been framed!\NThat's the only explanation for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] What's wrong with you, Light Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're saying is completely absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, for some reason,\Nit feels believable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You have to let me out!\NWe're wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] We can't let you out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like Light at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's contradicting himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't release him\Nnow that the murders have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, even I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't care what anyone says,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as I'm concerned,\Nwe have all the proof we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami is Kira\Nand that's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,FIFTEENTH DAY IN PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard two weeks’ worth of criminals\Nwere just murdered all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Kira is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA STRIKES AGAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you guys already tell the Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Chief?\NKira has started killing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Kira was only resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But now he has started\Npunishing criminals again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Is that true, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be happy\Nthat people have been killed but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,at least Light's name\Nwill finally be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, knowing Ryuzaki,\Nthis won't be enough to clear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda and Aizawa] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's in the gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what he just said, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Yeah, it's a hell of a lot better\Nthan being completely guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] I'm sure as grays go,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a shade closer to being cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's tell Light!\N-[L] Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, please don't, Mr. Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Matsuda"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't tell him about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What is it, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in here just over two weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and not a single new criminal\Nhas been punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why make this harder\Nthan it has to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if the evidence does point to me,\NI swear to you this is a set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoom in on me, if you want.\NGo ahead, look at my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,do these look like the eyes\Nof someone who's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Amane, are you ready to tell me\Nwho Kira is or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, if I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd thank him for punishing\Nthe burglar who killed my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, Kira is a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]